If you Ritual Summon exactly 1 "Nekroz" Ritual Monster, this card can be used as the entire Tribute. If this card is Tributed by a card effect: You can add 1 Warrior-Type "Nekroz" Ritual Monster from your Deck to your hand. You can only use this effect of "Shrit, Caster of the Nekroz" once per turn.
